:::The Protectrons:::

::The Master near the CF. Eventually the crew began to reactivate::
Chromedome: Uhh, everyone alright?
Highbrow: Im a-okay!
Brainstorm: Im alright!
Hardhead: Im fine.
Chromedome: Good, becuase were about to engage the enemy.
::They head toward the CF, where they see the Alliance attacking the CF::
Chromedome: Alright, spread out men, take whoever you can.
::The Protectrons split up and look for targets.
~~~~~
::Chromedome fired 25 laser blasts from each of his 2 guns at Dark One::
~~~~~
::Brainstorm fires 2 photon charges from each of his 2 guns at Breakdown::
~~~~~
::Highbrow fires a stream of acid from each of his 2 guns at Pyro::
~~~~~
::Hardhead fires 25 crystal shards from each of his 2 guns at Hiss::
